<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Schoenhuber Exploitation of Anti-Semitism Viewed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Schoenhuber Exploitation of Anti-Semitism Viewed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94EN0321B Frankfurt/Main FRANKFURTER RUNDSCHAU in German 23 
Apr 94 p 3 </F>

<F P=103> 94EN0321B </F>
<F P=104>  Frankfurt/Main FRANKFURTER RUNDSCHAU </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


