  [Text] Mozambique has asked Portugal to help with training 
its military police. The Maputo government and Renamo today 
asked Portugal to organize the new military police and to run 
another two leadership training programs for the new Mozambican 
Army. The Portuguese military mission in Mozambique has already 
come up with a specific program for training the police force 
and has already drawn up the curriculum for the new leadership 
courses. 

