<H4>    Holds Gas Supply Talks </H4>

<F P=102> LD0605134894 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1130 
GMT 6 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0605134894 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>
