<F P=104>  Berlin N-TV </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Torture in Turkey does not constitute adequate 
grounds for granting Kurds asylum. Under a verdict by the 
Federal Administrative Court in Berlin, Kurds in the Federal 
Republic can only claim asylum if they have no safe haven in 
Turkey. The court thus turned down an application for asylum by 
a Kurdish family from southeastern Turkey. [passage omitted] 

