  [Soares] No, I am not going to intercede, I am going to 
talk. 
I am going to try to talk -- it is not easy to talk to Savimbi, 
I have no direct channel of communication. He is the one who 
sometimes telephone me. I will see if I can ask him to 
telephone me. I would like to talk to him because this is 
definitely the time for peace. [end recording] 

</TEXT>

