<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Begins 3-Day Visit, Meets Weizsacker </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Begins 3-Day Visit, Meets Weizsacker </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1105093594 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network in German 0900 
GMT 11 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1105093594 </F>
<F P=104>  Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network </F>
