<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Russian President Boris Yeltsin arrived in Bonn 
this morning on a three-day official visit to Germany. 
President Richard von Weizsaecker received the visitor from 
Moscow, who is accompanied by Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev 
and Defense Minister Pavel Grachev. Yeltsin will then meet with 
Chancellor Helmut Kohl. [passage omitted] 

