<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Regional Governor Reports `Terrorist' Casualties </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Regional Governor Reports `Terrorist' Casualties </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1005183994 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 10 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1005183994 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Unal Erkan, state of emergency region governor, has 
announced that 150 terrorists were killed and 50 terrorists were 
captured in operations conducted in the state of emergency 
region in the past week. 
  Addressing the inauguration of the communications satellite 
ground station in Batman's Sason District, Erkan declared that 
the terrorist organization has reached the point of collapse as 
a result of the assistance the regional population has extended 
to the security forces in their joint struggle against 
terrorism. Pointing out that the number of terrorists 
surrendering to the security forces is increasing, despite the 
groundless propaganda that terrorists who surrender are 
mistreated, Erkan explained that the organization's sources of 
income from narcotics smuggling have also been wiped out. 

</TEXT>

