<H3> <TI>   WEU Ministers Plan To Dispatch Police to Mostar </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    WEU Ministers Plan To Dispatch Police to Mostar </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0905142894 Hamburg DPA in German 1242 GMT 9 May 94--FOR 
