  [Text] Brussels, 10 May (BELGA) -- According to a press 
release issued by the Belgian Foreign Ministry on Tuesday 
evening [10 May], Foreign Minister Willy Claes has met, at his 
request, with Faustin Twagiramungu, the Rwandan prime minister 
designated in the 4 August 1993 Arusha Accord. 
