  [Text] I have just learned that the 11 French people from 
the aid organization Premiere Urgence who are being detained in 
Bosnia could be released soon. This was said this morning by 
Radovan Karadzic, the Bosnian Serb leader. According to the 
Bosnian Serb agency SRNA [Serbian News Agency], the release 
could take place as soon as a legal formula has been found. 
[passage omitted] 

